---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Donate" description="Support the ongoing services and programs of Colorado Muslim Society.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container donate-layout">
      <h1>Donate</h1>
      <article class="card">
        <h2>Hadith</h2>
        <p>
          حَدَّثَنَا إِسْمَاعِيلُ، قَالَ حَدَّثَنِي أَخِي، عَنْ سُلَيْمَانَ، عَنْ مُعَاوِيَةَ بْنِ أَبِي
          مُزَرِّدٍ، عَنْ أَبِي الْحُبَابِ، عَنْ أَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ ـ رضى الله عنه ـ أَنَّ النَّبِيَّ صلى
          الله عليه وسلم قَالَ "مَا مِنْ يَوْمٍ يُصْبِحُ الْعِبَادُ فِيهِ إِلاَّ مَلَكَانِ يَنْزِلاَنِ
          فَيَقُولُ أَحَدُهُمَا اللَّهُمَّ أَعْطِ مُنْفِقًا خَلَفًا، وَيَقُولُ الآخَرُ اللَّهُمَّ أَعْطِ
          مُمْسِكًا تَلَفًا".
        </p>
        <p class="donate-hadith-en">
          Narrated Abu Huraira: The Prophet (ﷺ) said, "Every day two angels come down from Heaven and one
          of them says, 'O Allah! Compensate every person who spends in Your Cause,' and the other (angel)
          says, 'O Allah! Destroy every miser.'"
        </p>
        <p class="muted">Sahih al-Bukhari, 2:522</p>
      </article>
      <p class="donate-intro"></p>
      <div class="stack">
        <a
          class="btn btn-primary btn-donate"
          href="https://www.paypal.com/donate/?hosted_button_id=44JEQUVW4J68G"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer">Donate using Paypal or Credit/Debit Card</a
        >
      </div>
      <p class="muted donate-note">
        Thank you for choosing to donate to Colorado Muslim Society. Your generosity is appreciated and is
        IRS 501(c)(3) tax exempt. Your payments are securely handled by Paypal.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
